						   <div class="slider-text">
							   <h2>1st International Workshop on Solar Imaging with ALMA<br>
							   "ALMA-SOL-IMG1"</h2>
							   <h3>for encouraging millimeter/sub-millimeter solar sciences</h3>
						   </div>
					   </div>
